19:23.738 --> 19:34.028
organization of the chain. And I don't know how 
we'd survive without that, because if we didn't

19:34.666 --> 19:42.517
have that, everybody's going off on his own, just 
doing whatever he wants to do, you know. And I can

19:43.538 --> 19:50.849
perceive that, boy, there'd be clashes, and this 
guy's doing this, and this guy's doing that, and

19:43.538 --> 19:50.849
there'd be no... Which was the major thrust of the 
