We decided here at the College of Veterinary 
Medicine to go on a trimester system. We were on the

21:39.991 --> 21:43.136
semester system for four years. And this was 
during the time of sparsity and

21:47.995 --> 22:03.609
it was perceived that we needed to produce more 
